short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Allows to close all tabs to the left

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Too many tabs opened? Chrome allows to close all tabs to the right, close all tabs but current. But what about all tabs to the left? Tabs to the left are often was open earlier. This extension will help you to close already unnecessary tabs. Just click on extension's icon to close 'em.
